cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.NE 

This paper deals with ultrasound image compression using deep neural networks and physics modeling. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia). The use of compression algorithms and information theory could place it under cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also involves training a convolutional network, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the use of deep neural networks could also place it under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
